  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at 9th level, your melee weapon attacks and unarmed strikes score a critical hit on a roll of 19 or 20. Furthermore, you can roll one additional weapon damage die when determining the extra damage for a critical hit with a melee attack or ranged weapon that was thrown.</p><p>This increases to two additional dice at 13th level and three additional dice at 17th level.</p><p>Lastly, if you are raging you increase the damage of a critical hit with a melee weapon further by an amount equal to your Rage Damage, as shown on the Rage Damage column of the Barbarian table, per additional dice rolled.</p>",
